replies.msg:
Bernard Arnault: &quot;I don't know where do these rumors come. At one point Milanisti filled me with messages. I respect them a lot because I am a fan myself, but of PSG. Although I remember a beautiful Milan-Barcelona game in the Champions League in San Siro few years ago.&quot;<br />
<br />
Arnault: &quot;I am sorry to disappoint those who would have appreciated our investment, but it will not happen. We are already very present in Italy with prestigious brands and thousands of employees, we do not need Milan to expand.&quot;

